The Telegraph - Calcutta
 Kanpur keen to host Test vs NZ
Kanpur: Kanpur may after all get to host one of Indias two Tests against New Zealand in October this year after state sports officials and a BCCI Grounds and Wickets Committee member inspected the venue on Thursday. They decided to set things right in time for the match. We know the final decision whether Kanpur will host the match rests with the BCCI. But on our part we are in favour of hosting the match, state sports secretary R.C. Dua said.  (PTI)  Copyright 
